呀？你屋企人知唔知？ <br />\n允行：我唔知點同屋企人講呀。 <br />\n陳老師：一心，允行，傾咩咁開心呀？ <br />\n一心：允行佢想自殺但唔知點用屋企人講。 <br />\n陳老師：你可以寫封遺書比佢既。 <br />\n允行：陳老師，遺書格式係點架？ <br />\n陳老師：你可以用書信格式寫，記得交代你點解想自殺既兩個主要原因，我仲建議你可以寫父母點處理你既身後事既。 <br />\n<br />\n有咩閱讀材料用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum5.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=EP&amp;message=6299265&amp;highlight_id=0&amp;page=1&amp;authorOnly=False\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum5.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DEP%26message%3D6299265%26highlight_id%3D0%26page%3D1%26authorOnly%3DFalse&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=08e7da9f\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum5.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=EP&amp;message=6299265&amp;highlight_id=0&amp;page=1&amp;authorOnly=False</a>"},{"pid":"d1123a2d392a75817d7ec2b6fc5fd25b62b36e6b","tid":164032,"uid":14423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T13:49:00.000Z","msg":"文體：實用文"},{"pid":"44e5a43f6373b80589988b7c7483529b914dafb1","tid":164032,"uid":25869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T13:49:58.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d23145263e8c867b4495c0a37beb11993430eb","tid":164032,"uid":64290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T13:52:25.000Z","msg":"認真<br />\n寫遺書有咩要交代?<br />\n洗唔洗上款? 對象多過一個人要點寫?<br />\n係咪要寫日期先有法律效力?"},{"pid":"53e1c49371955b0872ec9a7af6fc195f4c0504dc","tid":164032,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T13:53:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"639fadc48acb6a4fb187c75cd7d936a49ccef2d4","tid":164032,"uid":61005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:02:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.